{"tid":1455150,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「撤 定 留」航班取消左蹬，然後呢？","createTime":"2019-08-12T08:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T08:45:25.000Z","uid":29979,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e960f57e4ec28eeb63a72cc0322c0dab03b30c62","tid":1455150,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:43:02.000Z","msg":"好似之前個post咁講，我地應該要set短期目標<br />\n<br />\n好似今次和你飛，航班停晒，係咪叫達成？<br />\n咁<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">然後呢？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n宜家有人<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">分析，無晒遊客，狗可能會清場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現場既你點睇？<br />\n係1516[size=5<span style=\"color: pink;\">]想留耐d爭取表態？</span>[/size=5]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">不了，留力下次</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">你，係做咩都得！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為你要自已決定！</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能你會見到現場「小朋友」叫你留低，跟住你諗諗<br />\n<br />\n可能你見到「鬼」怕無左你養唔到頭家<br />\n<br />\n但咩原因都好，請自己決定！無人想見到任何比人拉同受傷（狗隻除外）<br />\n<br />\n我明白大家都好不憤，但呢個時候「冷靜」先可以贏<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><br />\n總之「不割席，不分化」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uViyt9h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuViyt9h.jpg&h=dcb753d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jhP54HD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjhP54HD.png&h=eefa125f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4aee9341d4d1068478acdd6698ddd37ed03e44c","tid":1455150,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:44:33.000Z","msg":"自推 十下"},{"pid":"eefb53f7f975cb0989fd1bf2a8f0e418ac394826","tid":1455150,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:44:46.000Z","msg":"自推 九"},{"pid":"673f2b78f4ee586319a50d